    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Write a professional outreach email to the following contact:\n\nName: {{ $json.Name }}\nCompany: {{ $json.Company }}\nPurpose: {{ $json.Purpose }}\n\nRespond ONLY with valid JSON in this exact format — no markdown, no extra text:\n{\n  \"subject\": \"<compelling subject line>\",\n  \"body\": \"<complete HTML email — see requirements below>\"\n}\n\nHTML email requirements:\n- Use inline CSS only (no <style> tags, no external CSS)\n- Wrapper: <div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 15px;\">\n- Greeting and each paragraph wrapped in <p style=\"margin: 0 0 16px 0;\">\n- A <hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 24px 0;\"> before the signature\n- Signature block using these fictional but realistic sender details:\n  Name: James Whitfield\n  Title: Head of Partnerships\n  Company: NovaBridge Solutions\n  Email: j.whitfield@novabridge.io\n  Phone: +1 (415) 882-3301\n- Signature formatted as:\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#1a1a1a;\"><strong>James Whitfield</strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:2px 0;font-size:13px;color:#555;\">Head of Partnerships — NovaBridge Solutions</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:2px 0;font-size:13px;color:#555;\">j.whitfield@novabridge.io | +1 (415) 882-3301</p>\n- The email body must read as written by a real person — warm, specific, no generic filler phrases\n- 2–3 short focused paragraphs only\n- Do NOT use placeholder text like [Your Name] or [Your Company] anywhere",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are James Whitfield, Head of Partnerships at NovaBridge Solutions. You write sharp, human-sounding outreach emails that feel personal and credible — never robotic or templated. You always use the real sender details provided and never leave placeholder brackets. Respond with valid JSON only."
        }
      },
      "id": "3e097c22-8e62-4fd6-834d-bad5591f58ad",
      "name": "Generate Email Content",
